[[example]]
name = "tokio"
required-features = [ "tokio",]

[package]
name = "async-pipe"
version = "0.1.3"
description = "Creates an asynchronous piped reader and writer pair using tokio.rs"
homepage = "https://github.com/routerify/async-pipe-rs"
repository = "https://github.com/routerify/async-pipe-rs"
keywords = [ "pipe", "future", "async", "reader", "writer",]
categories = [ "asynchronous",]
authors = [ "Rousan Ali <rousanali786@gmail.com>",]
readme = "README.md"
license = "MIT"
edition = "2018"

[features]
default = [ "futures",]

[dependencies]
log = "0.4"

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1"
features = []
optional = true

[dependencies.futures]
version = "0.3"
optional = true

[dev-dependencies.tokio]
version = "1"
features = [ "full",]

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
features = [ "futures", "tokio",]

[package]
name = "blade-graphics"
version = "0.4.0"
edition = "2021"
description = "Graphics abstraction for Blade"
keywords = [ "graphics",]
license = "MIT"
repository = "https://github.com/kvark/blade"

[lib]

[dependencies]
bitflags = "2"
codespan-reporting = "0.11"
hidden-trait = "0.1"
log = "0.4"
mint = "0.5"
raw-window-handle = "0.5"

[dependencies.bytemuck]
version = "1"
features = [ "derive",]

[dependencies.naga]
features = [ "clone", "wgsl-in", "span", "validate",]
version = "0.14"

[package.metadata.cargo_check_external_types]
allowed_external_types = [ "bitflags::*", "mint::*", "naga::*", "raw_window_handle::*",]

[target."cfg(any(target_os = \"ios\", target_os = \"macos\"))".dependencies]
block = "0.1"
core-graphics-types = "0.1"
metal = "0.25"
objc = "0.2.5"

[target."cfg(any(vulkan, windows, target_os = \"linux\", target_os = \"android\"))".dependencies]
ash = "0.37"
ash-window = "0.12"
gpu-alloc = "0.6"
gpu-alloc-ash = "0.6"
slab = "0.4"

[target."cfg(any(gles, target_arch = \"wasm32\"))".dependencies]
glow = "0.13"

[target."cfg(all(target_arch = \"wasm32\"))".dependencies]
wasm-bindgen = "0.2.83"
js-sys = "0.3.60"

[target."cfg(any(target_os = \"ios\", target_os = \"macos\"))".dependencies.naga]
features = [ "msl-out", "wgsl-in", "span", "validate",]
version = "0.14"

[target."cfg(any(vulkan, windows, target_os = \"linux\", target_os = \"android\"))".dependencies.naga]
features = [ "spv-out", "wgsl-in", "span", "validate",]
version = "0.14"

[target."cfg(any(gles, target_arch = \"wasm32\"))".dependencies.naga]
features = [ "glsl-out", "wgsl-in", "span", "validate",]
version = "0.14"

[target."cfg(all(gles, not(target_arch = \"wasm32\")))".dependencies.egl]
package = "khronos-egl"
version = "5.0"
features = [ "dynamic",]

[target."cfg(all(gles, not(target_arch = \"wasm32\")))".dependencies.libloading]
version = "0.8"

[target."cfg(all(target_arch = \"wasm32\"))".dependencies.web-sys]
features = [ "HtmlCanvasElement", "WebGl2RenderingContext",]
version = "0.3.60"

[package]
name = "blade-macros"
version = "0.2.1"
edition = "2021"
description = "Macros helpers for Blade users"
keywords = [ "proc-macro",]
license = "MIT"
repository = "https://github.com/kvark/blade"

[lib]
proc-macro = true

[dependencies]
proc-macro2 = "1"
quote = "1.0"

[dev-dependencies]
mint = "0.5"

[dependencies.syn]
version = "2.0"
features = [ "full",]

[dev-dependencies.blade-graphics]
version = "0.4"
path = "../blade-graphics"

[dev-dependencies.blade-asset]
version = "0.2"
path = "../blade-asset"

[dev-dependencies.bytemuck]
version = "1"
features = [ "derive",]

[package]
name = "font-kit"
version = "0.11.0"
authors = [ "Patrick Walton <pcwalton@mimiga.net>",]
description = "A cross-platform font loading library"
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
readme = "README.md"
repository = "https://github.com/servo/font-kit"
homepage = "https://github.com/servo/font-kit"
exclude = [ "resources/**",]
edition = "2018"

[features]
default = [ "source",]
loader-freetype = [ "freetype",]
loader-freetype-default = [ "loader-freetype",]
source-fontconfig = [ "yeslogic-fontconfig-sys",]
source-fontconfig-dlopen = [ "yeslogic-fontconfig-sys/dlopen",]
source-fontconfig-default = [ "source-fontconfig",]
source = []

[dependencies]
bitflags = "1"
byteorder = "1.2"
float-ord = "0.2"
lazy_static = "1.1"
libc = "0.2"
log = "0.4.4"
pathfinder_geometry = "0.5"
pathfinder_simd = "0.5.1"

[dev-dependencies]
clap = "2.32"
colored = "1.6"
pbr = "1.0"
prettytable-rs = "0.10"

[dependencies.freetype]
version = "0.7"
optional = true

[dependencies.yeslogic-fontconfig-sys]
version = "3.0.0"
optional = true

[target."cfg(any(target_os = \"macos\", target_os = \"ios\"))".dependencies]
core-foundation = "0.9"
core-graphics = "0.23"
core-text = "20.1"

[target."cfg(not(any(target_family = \"windows\", target_os = \"macos\", target_os = \"ios\")))".dependencies]
freetype = "0.7"

[target."cfg(not(any(target_family = \"windows\", target_os = \"macos\", target_os = \"ios\", target_arch = \"wasm32\")))".dependencies]
yeslogic-fontconfig-sys = "3.0.0"

[target."cfg(not(any(target_arch = \"wasm32\", target_family = \"windows\", target_os = \"android\")))".dependencies]
dirs-next = "2.0"

[target."cfg(not(target_arch = \"wasm32\"))".dependencies]
walkdir = "2.1"

[target."cfg(target_family = \"windows\")".dependencies.dwrote]
version = "0.11"
default-features = false

[target."cfg(target_family = \"windows\")".dependencies.winapi]
version = "0.3"
features = [ "dwrite", "minwindef", "sysinfoapi", "winbase", "winnt",]

[[example]]
name = "rmp-serde"
required-features = [ "serde-rmp",]

[package]
name = "heed"
version = "0.20.0-alpha.9"
authors = [ "Kerollmops <renault.cle@gmail.com>",]
description = "A fully typed LMDB wrapper with minimum overhead"
license = "MIT"
repository = "https://github.com/Kerollmops/heed"
keywords = [ "lmdb", "database", "storage", "typed",]
categories = [ "database", "data-structures",]
readme = "../README.md"
edition = "2021"

[dependencies]
libc = "0.2.139"
once_cell = "1.16.0"
page_size = "0.6.0"
synchronoise = "1.0.1"

[dev-dependencies]
tempfile = "3.3.0"

[features]
default = [ "serde", "serde-bincode", "serde-json",]
serde = [ "bitflags/serde", "dep:serde",]
read-txn-no-tls = []
serde-bincode = [ "heed-types/serde-bincode",]
serde-json = [ "heed-types/serde-json",]
serde-rmp = [ "heed-types/serde-rmp",]
preserve_order = [ "heed-types/preserve_order",]
arbitrary_precision = [ "heed-types/arbitrary_precision",]
raw_value = [ "heed-types/raw_value",]
unbounded_depth = [ "heed-types/unbounded_depth",]
posix-sem = [ "lmdb-master-sys/posix-sem",]
mdb_idl_logn_8 = [ "lmdb-master-sys/mdb_idl_logn_8",]
mdb_idl_logn_9 = [ "lmdb-master-sys/mdb_idl_logn_9",]
mdb_idl_logn_10 = [ "lmdb-master-sys/mdb_idl_logn_10",]
mdb_idl_logn_11 = [ "lmdb-master-sys/mdb_idl_logn_11",]
mdb_idl_logn_12 = [ "lmdb-master-sys/mdb_idl_logn_12",]
mdb_idl_logn_13 = [ "lmdb-master-sys/mdb_idl_logn_13",]
mdb_idl_logn_14 = [ "lmdb-master-sys/mdb_idl_logn_14",]
mdb_idl_logn_15 = [ "lmdb-master-sys/mdb_idl_logn_15",]
mdb_idl_logn_16 = [ "lmdb-master-sys/mdb_idl_logn_16",]

[dependencies.bitflags]
version = "2.3.3"
features = [ "serde",]

[dependencies.byteorder]
version = "1.4.3"
default-features = false

[dependencies.heed-traits]
version = "0.20.0-alpha.9"
path = "../heed-traits"

[dependencies.heed-types]
version = "0.20.0-alpha.9"
default-features = false
path = "../heed-types"

[dependencies.lmdb-master-sys]
version = "0.1.0"
path = "../lmdb-master-sys"

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.151"
features = [ "derive",]
optional = true

[dev-dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.151"
features = [ "derive",]

[target."cfg(windows)".dependencies]
url = "2.3.1"

[package]
name = "heed-traits"
version = "0.20.0-alpha.9"
authors = [ "Kerollmops <renault.cle@gmail.com>",]
description = "The traits used inside of the fully typed LMDB wrapper, heed"
license = "MIT"
repository = "https://github.com/Kerollmops/heed"
readme = "../README.md"
edition = "2021"

[dependencies]

[package]
name = "heed-types"
version = "0.20.0-alpha.9"
authors = [ "Kerollmops <renault.cle@gmail.com>",]
description = "The types used with the fully typed LMDB wrapper, heed"
license = "MIT"
repository = "https://github.com/Kerollmops/heed"
readme = "../README.md"
edition = "2021"

[dependencies]
byteorder = "1.4.3"

[features]
default = [ "serde-bincode", "serde-json",]
serde-bincode = [ "serde", "bincode",]
serde-json = [ "serde", "serde_json",]
serde-rmp = [ "serde", "rmp-serde",]
preserve_order = [ "serde_json/preserve_order",]
arbitrary_precision = [ "serde_json/arbitrary_precision",]
raw_value = [ "serde_json/raw_value",]
unbounded_depth = [ "serde_json/unbounded_depth",]

[dependencies.bincode]
version = "1.3.3"
optional = true

[dependencies.heed-traits]
version = "0.20.0-alpha.9"
path = "../heed-traits"

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.151"
optional = true

[dependencies.serde_json]
version = "1.0.91"
optional = true

[dependencies.rmp-serde]
version = "1.1.2"
optional = true

[package]
name = "lmdb-master-sys"
version = "0.1.0"
authors = [ "Kerollmops <clement@meilisearch.com>", "Dan Burkert <dan@danburkert.com>", "Victor Porof <vporof@mozilla.com>",]
license = "Apache-2.0"
description = "Rust bindings for liblmdb on the mdb.master branch."
documentation = "https://docs.rs/lmdb-master-sys"
repository = "https://github.com/meilisearch/heed/tree/main/lmdb-master-sys"
readme = "README.md"
keywords = [ "LMDB", "database", "storage-engine", "bindings", "library",]
categories = [ "database", "external-ffi-bindings",]
edition = "2021"
build = "build.rs"

[lib]
name = "lmdb_master_sys"
doctest = false

[dependencies]
libc = "0.2.139"

[build-dependencies]
cc = "1.0.78"
doxygen-rs = "0.4.2"

[dev-dependencies]
cstr = "0.2.11"

[features]
default = []
asan = []
fuzzer = []
fuzzer-no-link = []
posix-sem = []
mdb_idl_logn_8 = []
mdb_idl_logn_9 = []
mdb_idl_logn_10 = []
mdb_idl_logn_11 = []
mdb_idl_logn_12 = []
mdb_idl_logn_13 = []
mdb_idl_logn_14 = []
mdb_idl_logn_15 = []
mdb_idl_logn_16 = []

[build-dependencies.bindgen]
version = "0.69.1"
default-features = false
optional = true
features = [ "runtime",]

[package]
name = "lsp-types"
version = "0.94.1"
authors = [ "Markus Westerlind <marwes91@gmail.com>", "Bruno Medeiros <bruno.do.medeiros@gmail.com>",]
edition = "2018"
description = "Types for interaction with a language server, using VSCode's Language Server Protocol"
repository = "https://github.com/gluon-lang/lsp-types"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/lsp-types"
readme = "README.md"
keywords = [ "language", "server", "lsp", "vscode", "lsif",]
license = "MIT"

[dependencies]
bitflags = "1.0.1"
serde_json = "1.0.50"
serde_repr = "0.1"

[features]
default = []
proposed = []

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.34"
features = [ "derive",]

[dependencies.url]
version = "2.0.0"
features = [ "serde",]

[[bench]]
name = "rpc_tokio"
harness = false
required-features = [ "use_tokio",]

[[example]]
name = "handler_drop"
required-features = [ "use_tokio",]

[[example]]
name = "quitting"
required-features = [ "use_tokio",]

[[example]]
name = "scorched_earth"
required-features = [ "use_tokio",]

[[example]]
name = "basic"
required-features = [ "use_tokio",]

[[example]]
name = "bench_tokio"
required-features = [ "use_tokio",]

[[example]]
name = "bench_async-std"
required-features = [ "use_async-std",]

[[example]]
name = "bench_sync"
required-features = [ "use_neovim_lib",]

[[example]]
name = "scorched_earth_as"
required-features = [ "use_async-std",]

[[example]]
name = "nested_requests"
required-features = [ "use_tokio",]

[[test]]
name = "nested_requests"
required-features = [ "use_tokio",]

[[test]]
name = "connecting"
path = "tests/connecting/mod.rs"

[[test]]
name = "notifications"
required-features = [ "use_tokio",]

[[test]]
name = "basic"

[package]
name = "nvim-rs"
version = "0.6.0-pre"
license = "LGPL-3.0"
authors = [ "KillTheMule <KillTheMule@users.noreply.github.com",]
description = "A library for writing neovim rpc clients"
repository = "https://github.com/KillTheMule/nvim-rs"
readme = "README.md"
categories = [ "api-bindings",]
keywords = [ "neovim", "nvim", "rpc", "msgpack",]
exclude = [ "neovim/*", ".travis.yml", "appveyor.yml", ".git", ".gitignore", ".gitmodules", "build.ps1",]
edition = "2021"

[features]
use_tokio = [ "tokio", "tokio-util", "parity-tokio-ipc",]
use_async-std = [ "async-std",]
use_neovim_lib = [ "neovim-lib",]

[lib]
bench = false

[dependencies]
rmp = "0.8.12"
rmpv = "1.0.1"
log = "0.4.20"
async-trait = "0.1.73"

[dev-dependencies]
tempfile = "3.8.0"
fastrand = "2.0.0"
criterion = "0.5.1"

[dependencies.futures]
version = "0.3.28"
features = [ "io-compat",]

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.32.0"
features = [ "full",]
optional = true

[dependencies.tokio-util]
version = "0.7.8"
features = [ "compat",]
optional = true

[dependencies.async-std]
version = "1.12.0"
features = [ "attributes",]
optional = true

[dependencies.neovim-lib]
version = "0.6.1"
optional = true

[dependencies.parity-tokio-ipc]
version = "0.9.0"
optional = true

[profile.bench]
lto = true
debug = true

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
features = [ "use_tokio",]
rustdoc-args = [ "--cfg", "docsrs",]

[package]
name = "pathfinder_simd"
version = "0.5.3"
edition = "2018"
authors = [ "Patrick Walton <pcwalton@mimiga.net>",]
build = "build.rs"
description = "A simple SIMD library"
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
repository = "https://github.com/servo/pathfinder"
homepage = "https://github.com/servo/pathfinder"

[features]
pf-no-simd = []

[dependencies]

[build-dependencies]
rustc_version = "0.4"

[[bench]]
name = "dummy_benchmark"
path = "benches/dummy_benchmark.rs"
harness = false

[package]
name = "taffy"
version = "0.3.11"
authors = [ "Alice Cecile <alice.i.cecile@gmail.com>", "Johnathan Kelley <jkelleyrtp@gmail.com>",]
edition = "2021"
rust-version = "1.65"
include = [ "src/**/*", "Cargo.toml", "README.md",]
description = "A flexible UI layout library "
repository = "https://github.com/DioxusLabs/taffy"
keywords = [ "cross-platform", "layout", "flexbox", "css-grid", "grid",]
categories = [ "gui",]
license = "MIT"

[features]
default = [ "std", "flexbox", "grid", "block_layout", "taffy_tree",]
block_layout = []
flexbox = []
grid = [ "alloc", "dep:grid",]
alloc = []
std = [ "num-traits/std", "grid?/std",]
serde = [ "dep:serde",]
debug = [ "std",]
profile = [ "std",]
taffy_tree = [ "dep:slotmap",]

[dev-dependencies]
serde_json = "1.0.93"

[workspace]
members = [ "scripts/gentest", "scripts/format-fixtures", "scripts/import-yoga-tests", "benches",]

[dependencies.arrayvec]
version = "0.7"
default-features = false

[dependencies.num-traits]
version = "0.2"
default-features = false

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
optional = true
features = [ "serde_derive",]

[dependencies.slotmap]
version = "1.0.6"
optional = true

[dependencies.grid]
version = "0.11.0"
default-features = false
optional = true

[dev-dependencies.taffy]
path = "."

[profile.release]
lto = true
panic = "abort"

[package]
name = "tree-sitter"
version = "0.20.100"
description = "Rust bindings to the Tree-sitter parsing library"
publish = false
authors = [ "Max Brunsfeld <maxbrunsfeld@gmail.com>",]
edition = "2021"
rust-version = "1.65"
readme = "binding_rust/README.md"
homepage = "https://tree-sitter.github.io/tree-sitter"
repository = "https://github.com/tree-sitter/tree-sitter"
license = "MIT"
keywords = [ "incremental", "parsing",]
categories = [ "api-bindings", "parsing", "text-editors",]
build = "binding_rust/build.rs"
links = "tree-sitter"
include = [ "/binding_rust/*", "/Cargo.toml", "/src/*.h", "/src/*.c", "/src/unicode/*", "/src/wasm/*", "/include/tree_sitter/api.h",]

[features]
wasm = [ "wasmtime-c-api",]

[dependencies]
regex = "1.10.3"

[build-dependencies]
cc = "1.0.90"

[lib]
path = "binding_rust/lib.rs"

[dependencies.wasmtime-c-api]
version = "19"
optional = true
package = "wasmtime-c-api-impl"
default-features = false

[build-dependencies.bindgen]
version = "0.69.4"
optional = true

[package]
name = "tree-sitter-bash"
description = "Bash grammar for tree-sitter"
version = "0.20.4"
authors = [ "Max Brunsfeld <maxbrunsfeld@gmail.com",]
license = "MIT"
readme = "bindings/rust/README.md"
keywords = [ "incremental", "parsing", "bash",]
categories = [ "parsing", "text-editors",]
repository = "https://github.com/tree-sitter/tree-sitter-bash"
edition = "2021"
autoexamples = false
build = "bindings/rust/build.rs"
include = [ "bindings/rust/*", "grammar.js", "queries/*", "src/*",]

[lib]
path = "bindings/rust/lib.rs"

[dependencies]
tree-sitter = "~0.20.10"

[build-dependencies]
cc = "~1.0.83"

[package]
name = "tree-sitter-cpp"
description = "Cpp grammar for the tree-sitter parsing library"
version = "0.20.0"
authors = [ "Max Brunsfeld <maxbrunsfeld@gmail.com>",]
license = "MIT"
readme = "bindings/rust/README.md"
keywords = [ "incremental", "parsing", "cpp",]
categories = [ "parsing", "text-editors",]
repository = "https://github.com/tree-sitter/tree-sitter-cpp"
edition = "2018"
build = "bindings/rust/build.rs"
include = [ "bindings/rust/*", "grammar.js", "queries/*", "src/*",]

[lib]
path = "bindings/rust/lib.rs"

[dependencies]
tree-sitter = "0.20"

[build-dependencies]
cc = "1.0"

[package]
name = "tree-sitter-css"
description = "css grammar for the tree-sitter parsing library"
version = "0.19.0"
keywords = [ "incremental", "parsing", "css",]
categories = [ "parsing", "text-editors",]
repository = "https://github.com/tree-sitter/tree-sitter-javascript"
edition = "2018"
license = "MIT"
authors = [ "Max Brunsfeld <maxbrunsfeld@gmail.com>",]
build = "bindings/rust/build.rs"
include = [ "bindings/rust/*", "grammar.js", "queries/*", "src/*",]

[lib]
path = "bindings/rust/lib.rs"

[dependencies]
tree-sitter = ">= 0.19"

[build-dependencies]
cc = "1.0"

[package]
name = "tree-sitter-elixir"
description = "Elixir grammar for the tree-sitter parsing library"
version = "0.1.0"
keywords = [ "incremental", "parsing", "elixir",]
categories = [ "parsing", "text-editors",]
repository = "https://github.com/elixir-lang/tree-sitter-elixir"
edition = "2018"
license = "Apache-2.0"
build = "bindings/rust/build.rs"
include = [ "bindings/rust/*", "grammar.js", "queries/*", "src/*",]

[lib]
path = "bindings/rust/lib.rs"

[dependencies]
tree-sitter = ">= 0.19, < 0.21"

[build-dependencies]
cc = "1.0"

[package]
name = "tree-sitter-go"
description = "Go grammar for the tree-sitter parsing library"
version = "0.19.1"
authors = [ "Max Brunsfeld <maxbrunsfeld@gmail.com>", "Douglas Creager <dcreager@dcreager.net>",]
license = "MIT"
readme = "bindings/rust/README.md"
keywords = [ "incremental", "parsing", "go",]
categories = [ "parsing", "text-editors",]
repository = "https://github.com/tree-sitter/tree-sitter-go"
edition = "2018"
build = "bindings/rust/build.rs"
include = [ "bindings/rust/*", "grammar.js", "queries/*", "src/*",]

[lib]
path = "bindings/rust/lib.rs"

[dependencies]
tree-sitter = ">= 0.19, < 0.21"

[build-dependencies]
cc = "1.0"

[package]
name = "tree-sitter-gomod"
description = "gomod grammar for the tree-sitter parsing library"
version = "1.0.2"
keywords = [ "incremental", "parsing", "gomod",]
categories = [ "parsing", "text-editors",]
repository = "https://github.com/camdencheek/tree-sitter-go-mod"
edition = "2018"
